        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I don't think this fixes #25619. I built the branch on Win 10 and used Cygwin (mintty 3.8.2) + bash; still saw it clear contents after quitting.\r\n\r\nBefore:\r\n<img width=\"902\" height=\"625\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/aaf3eb97-7054-4af7-8a48-b2787834a70e\" />\r\n\r\nAfter:\r\n<img width=\"901\" height=\"324\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f5ac4d3a-56ae-4373-b3a4-26b1a340d0c6\" />\r\n\r\nI also ran some tests with nvim 0.12.2.\r\n- win10 + cygwin (mintty) + powershell: worked\r\n- win11 + conemu + powershell: worked\r\n- win11 + cygwin (mintty) + bash: didn't work (cleared screen)\r\n- win11 + cygwin (mintty) + powershell: worked\r\n\r\nSo it seems related to the shell somehow too.\r\n\r\nEDIT: I did test the cursor styling as well, which works on Windows Terminal and ConEmu.",
